snippet.textDisplay: Me too! The migraines were on a scale of 10. I’d get physically sick just by trying to wander into the kitchen. I had the night sweats to where I put towels under my pjs. I smelled things really in a weird way. Fever broke exactly 5 days from the first symptom. It was more annoying than actually scary. But I was fully vaccinated and had one booster. I didn’t need to go to the hospital because I was able to ride it out at home. Just got another booster 2 days ago. But that’s my choice. I don’t push vaccines onto anyone’s personal choices. Be safe whichever way you choose to be. 🕊
